{
  "stem": "9665.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- and we went for a round-- you know, a fully fashioned machine, we changed it into round machines, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if you understand it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, circle machines, because you're not wearing anything with a seam here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were fully fashioned machines, but with a seam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyway-- so then, we bought this factory in Adelaide-- in Adelaide-- in-- what am I talking about?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In Sydney, in Leichhardt, which was the national hosiery mill, which was with fully fashioned-- it was not fully fashioned.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They also had fully fashioned machines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We threw them out, and we had circle machines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were the first one in Australia and in the world to make pantyhose.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We first had-- if you remember that-- this was before your time-- which were called the 'stay-ups'-- which were some stay-ups.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We made the circular pantyhose, the circular stockings, then, later on, circular machines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was an enormous success.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Enormous success.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were very successful, after I got rid of the Liebermans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Liebermans-- I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were very nice people, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm sure they are very nice, but I'm happy I was with Jan Laos.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Unfortunately, he got a heart problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Jan Laos got a heart problem in 1966 or '67 and had to leave the company.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We acquired Glomesh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We acquired Rocktex, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We acquired-- we-- well, we didn't acquire that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We made our own yarn mill in Seven Hills.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were the most successful-- we were the gold stock on the stock exchange.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was Kolotex.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then, one day, it happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was 1973 that the people which got the first really money from us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we joined them, the Liebermans, they didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were just bluffing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
